---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Repo Wave" description="Learn more about who we are and our mission to make open-source accessible.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-8 md:p-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">About Us</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600 space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            We are a team of open-source enthusiasts and developers dedicated to bridging the gap between open-source maintainers and contributors. Over the years, we noticed how difficult it was for beginners to find the right issues and repositories to make their first contributions. Realizing the immense value that open-source software brings to the world, we decided to create a platform that makes this process intuitive and welcoming.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What Our Website Does</h2>
          <p>
            Repo Wave is designed specifically to help developers easily discover top open-source repositories and beginner-friendly issues. By curating a feed of accessible tasks across various languages, we lower the barrier to entry for contributing. We aggregate active issues that are explicitly labeled as beginner-friendly, good first issue, or help wanted, empowering you to find projects that perfectly match your skills and interests.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
          <ul class="list-none space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mr-3 mt-1">1</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">AI scores issues</strong> across 100 repos</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mr-3 mt-1">2</span>
              <p class="text-gray-700"><strong class="text-gray-900">Dashboard filters</strong> your perfect matches</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            Our ultimate mission is to foster a more inclusive and vibrant open-source community. We want to make open-source contribution accessible to everyone, from novice programmers writing their first lines of code to seasoned developers looking to explore new ecosystems. By helping developers connect with projects they care about, we hope to accelerate learning and support the ecosystem that powers modern software development.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
